{"type": "article", "id": 54478, "title": "这个为自行车设计的车库，室内室外都能使用｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-20T23:22:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47963, "name": "Erik Jørgensen"}, {"id": 51259, "name": "Eric G. Pearson"}, {"id": 51260, "name": "Damian Williamson f"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 163, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180620232447VfJPjKr4c2syCbLu.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: #657ab7} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: #657ab7} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: #657ab7; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Alpen Bike Capsule by Eric G. Pearson</h3><p>汽车有专用车库，但自行车的停放基本上都是依赖于自行车架，它并不是理想的存放自行车的专用空间。这促使设计师 Eric G. Pearson 创造了 Alpen，他推出了一款专门针对骑行爱好者的便捷自行车车库，可以有效防止你的爱车被风吹日晒雨淋所侵袭。</p><p>它由坚韧的旋转模制聚乙烯制成，并配备了集成的锁定结构。它框架小巧，造型时尚，室内外皆可放置，当然前提是你的房子够大。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232530dprslfqJPOYHDXU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806202325306NXaPnKUbH2Dt9hl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232530lBL4EZAPS9sWN2jk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806202325303NnhIT48rsodmBce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018062023253186IxLyebH7P0rqES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232531MugjhoyNx2BO5PAq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.alpenstorage.com/checkout/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alpen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ovo Chair by by Damian Williamson for Erik Jørgensen</h3><p>英国设计师 Damian Williamson 为丹麦家具品牌 Erik Jørgensen 设计了一款名为 Ovo 的座椅，据称其灵感源自在面板上正在新鲜擀制的意大利面是如何折叠的，Ovo 这个名字来源于意大利语 Uovo，意思是鸡蛋。</p><p>Ovo 座椅由超大靠背和两个扶手面板构成。靠背与扶手的大尺寸是 Ovo 最吸引人的特点，底部细细钢条支撑的方形钢架，上部是大体量的软垫元素，材料和线条之间的碰撞与对比，反而实现了某种和谐的平衡感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232630h5SXUkGzE3trKZ26.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232632mvbPy7ztQ0uFlwZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232632b0AKvNaDSEwuicgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LARQ Bottle by Justin Wang</h3><p>分辨清洁和肮脏的水很简单，但区分水的新鲜程度，并不是肉眼可见就能辨识的。设计师 Justin Wang 给出了一个创新解决方案 LARQ Bottle。</p><p>这是一个石英水瓶，能够通过紫外线喷射有害微生物，一天可以帮助瓶子及其内部盛装的水消毒 6 次。它的工作原理和任何保温瓶一样，尺寸适宜，宽口径，便于冲洗瓶子内部，玄机藏在盖子部位，这个盖子内嵌了医疗级紫外线，以 280nm 的波长照射瓶子内部，杀死细菌的同时保持无味。</p><p>紫外灯每四小时启动一次，也可以由用户主动选择启动，60 秒内完成净化。目前，LARQ 水瓶在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上的众筹价是 59 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/443292702/quartz-bottle?ref=853k6f&amp;utm_source=website&amp;utm_medium=Yanko&amp;utm_campaign=KS&amp;utm_content=YD_Website\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232710GvSEkA2RtVdQJ6B7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806202327101ewSm9ctLFa3jOvy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232710YlKva8WTSBUQpdjg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232710lkmhJADP3HCMn0Q5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806202327103Yt4KQ8CFa0HXPN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232710NWtTaPyoL1uJh5DG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232710yZoc8KTEqj9eHfnv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806202327105pLxH9MIKZz6UmAc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Repair Pens by Blufixx</h3><p>很多人可能都会遇到这样的问题，手机的数据线用久了就会坏掉，大多数时候，数据线损坏的原因是由于插头和线缆之间接头处的磨损，不少用户会选择用胶带缠一下继续使用，或是干脆换根新线。</p><p>Blufixx 是一款数据线专用的修复笔，它具有重塑和保护低压线缆的功能。用户们只需要在数据线的磨损处涂上一层修复胶水，然后再使用附带的 LED 灯照射该位置 3 至 5 秒，待胶水干了之后即可使用。</p><p>此外，它还可以修复耳机线和游戏柄线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812VkaY9iNfTMWpyPQg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812YAZX6I5wKRsTOJoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812uR9Dvb5Hc1gdKojr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812lujLOmo3ZdtfINA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812yhIvSQFic8zNJqfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232812Z0VCpuJrOk1hTQwH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Octo by Sipyeong Lee &amp; Jungbin Oh</h3><p>设计师 Sipyeong Lee 和 Jungbin Oh 认为，人们谈论产品设计时，常常喜欢追求所谓形式和功能的完美平衡，却忘记了自然本能，以及如何简单地享受它。</p><p>Octo 是一款可爱的小玩意儿，这是一款酱油容器，样子像是喷射墨水的章鱼，使用 起来简单直接。它由两个红色、白色酱油小瓶组成，模拟章鱼变色的情绪。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232856FAG15Rlf0ma9inOs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232856tcLwTPjBoUz2Dk8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232857XZELc7t2SFype1C4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232857w9moxa6cfV34Yzv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232857CX17P5AMJfVElYzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232857p38Ha057yjfs1MqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180620232857usdawKGp0l5eShXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}